title: Mathematica by Example - Martha L. Abell, James P. Braselton
description:
Mathematica by Example - Martha L. Abell, James P. Braselton (Academic Press, 1992).pdf

ISBN 0120415402

This work is designed to act as a supplementary text for those using or beginning to use Mathematica, the sophisticated mathematical software system. Topics covered include calculus, linear algebra, ordinary and partial differential equations, discrete mathematics and more
